page21.title: Lily
page21.content: Once upon a time, in a small village nestled in the heart of a dense forest, there lived a young girl named Lily. She had long curly hair that fell in gentle waves down her back and eyes that shone like emeralds. Lily lived with her parents, who were both carpenters, in a small wooden cottage at the edge of the forest.  Lily was a curious and adventurous girl, and she loved nothing more than exploring the woods around her home. One day, as she was wandering through the trees, she stumbled upon a hidden clearing. In the center of the clearing stood an old, gnarled tree that was unlike any she had ever seen before.And the end!. But it was not the end the story continues....
